Revision history for Net-DNS-CloudFlare-DDNS

v0.63.1   2016-03-28
 - Test with TravisCI
 - use new interface of CloudFlare::Client
 - update dist.ini
 - Move to github
 - switch to V-string
 - Fix previous version changelog
 - Changes to work with Pod::Weave / Test::Synopsis properly

0.06_3    2014-10-02
 - Fix more bugs
 - Bits and bobs
 - Update repo info - git repo split

0.06_2    2014-08-26
 - Fix bugs

0.06_1    2014-08-19
 - Moo -> Moose
 - add no indirect 'fatal'
 - Zone IDs are updated per each batch of updates so online changes to DNS
   don't cause problems
 - Failures are handled per DNS record update
 - Rewrite to be resilient and fault tolerant. Failures of any expected type
   handled without dying
 - Rewrite to use CloudFlare::Client
 - Use IP lookup services in a random order
 - Use Dist::Zilla to build

